  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "CHEF",
  "description": "<p>Our Chinese restaurant specializing is looking for an experienced and passionate <strong>Chef</strong> to join our team. The ideal candidate should be skilled in authentic Sichuan-style cooking, able to design flavorful and creative menus, and lead the kitchen team to maintain high food quality standards.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Plan and develop authentic menus, considering cost, taste, and seasonal ingredients.</li><li>Supervise and manage daily kitchen operations.</li><li>Ensure all dishes are prepared and presented according to restaurant standards.</li><li>Train and guide kitchen staff in cooking techniques and hygiene practices.</li><li>Monitor stock levels, ingredients, and kitchen supplies; place orders as needed.</li><li>Maintain high standards of cleanliness and food safety in the kitchen.</li><li>Innovate and introduce new dishes to keep the menu attractive.</li><li>Handle feedback from customers and improve where necessary.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Proven experience as a <strong>Chef</strong>, preferably in a Korean<strong> restaurant</strong>.</li><li>Strong knowledge of<strong> cooking techniques and flavors</strong>.</li><li>Excellent leadership and communication skills.</li><li>Able to work efficiently under pressure and handle multiple tasks.</li><li>High standards of food quality, hygiene, and presentation.</li><li>Passion for creating delicious and authentic Chinese dishes.</li></ul>",
